msg: Convert all of the callback wrapper methods in the Python bindings
to be instance methods instead of static methods, so that they don't
need to mess with batons anymore.
WC.status, WC.info, Stream.__init__): Don't pass self as baton.
Stream._read, Stream._write, Stream._close): Convert from static
methods into instance methods. Ignore batons.
